<html>
  <head>
    <script language="JavaScript">
      var baseUrl = "<%= baseUrl %>";
    </script>
    <script src="<%= baseUrl %>libs/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="<%= baseUrl %>libs/socket.io.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="<%= baseUrl %>lobby.js"></script>
    <script
      type="text/javascript"
      src="<%= baseUrl %>libs/bootstrap.min.js"
    ></script>
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      type="text/css"
      href="<%= baseUrl %>libs/bootstrap.min.css"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="<%= baseUrl %>game.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="<%= baseUrl %>lobby.css" />
    <title>NodeLudo - Lobby</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="panel-heading">
        <div style="padding: 0; align-content: center">
          <button style="width: 150px" id="logoutBtn">Change nickname</button>
          <div
            style="text-align: center; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 -30px 150px"
            class="title"
          >
            <div class="title-red">L</div>
            <div class="title-green">u</div>
            <div class="title-yellow">d</div>
            <div class="title-blue">o</div>
            <div class="title-green">-</div>
            <div class="title-blue">K</div>
            <div class="title-red">i</div>
            <div class="title-green">n</div>
            <div class="title-yellow">G</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row" style="top: 50%">
      <div
        class="lobby-box col-xs-12 col-xs-offset-0 col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 col-xl-4 col-xl-offset-4"
      >
        <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-heading"><b>Players in lobby</b></div>
          <div class="panel-body">
            <div id="players"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row" style="top: 50%">
      <div
        class="lobby-box col-xs-12 col-xs-offset-0 col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 col-xl-4 col-xl-offset-4"
      >
        <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-heading"><b>Ready Players</b></div>
          <div class="panel-body">
            <div id="readyPlayers"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="panel-footer">
            <div>
              <button id="startGame" style="width: 27%">Start Game</button>
              <button id="readyBtn" style="width: 20%">Ready</button>
              <button id="addBotBtn" style="width: 21%">Add bot</button>
              <button id="removeBotBtn" style="width: 28%">Remove bot</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div
        class="lobby-box col-xs-12 col-xs-offset-0 col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 col-xl-4 col-xl-offset-4"
      >
        <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-heading">
            <b
              >Ongoing games
              <div id="ongoingGamesNumber" style="display: inline"></div
            ></b>
          </div>
          <div
            id="ongoingGames"
            class="panel-body"
            style="overflow: auto; max-height: 380px; min-height: 20px"
          ></div>
          <div class="panel-footer">Click on a game to spectate.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div
        class="lobby-box col-xs-12 col-xs-offset-0 col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 col-xl-4 col-xl-offset-4"
      >
        <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-heading">
            <b
              >Previous games
              <div id="previousGamesNumber" style="display: inline"></div
            ></b>
          </div>
          <div
            id="previousGames"
            class="panel-body"
            style="overflow: auto; max-height: 480px; min-height: 20px"
          ></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div
        class="lobby-box col-xs-12 col-xs-offset-0 col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 col-xl-4 col-xl-offset-4"
      >
        <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-heading"><b>Regler</b></div>
          <div class="panel-body">
            <ol>
              <li>
                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit.
                Consequuntur corporis inventore dolor! Culpa, neque unde
                asperiores obcaecati ipsam sequi natus perferendis, repudiandae
                repellendus nostrum in odit explicabo, eveniet earum id.
              </li>
            </ol>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="page-footer font-small pt-4">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-offset-3 col-xs-6">
          <div class="footer-copyright text-center py-3">
            Made by 

          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-3">
          <div style="float: right">
            Version:
            <a
              id="patch-notes"
              data-toggle="popover"
              data-trigger="focus"
              tabindex="0"
              title="Patch notes"
              data-placement="top"
              data-content="<% include patch-notes.ejs %>"
              >0.1.31</a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
